{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775868884632,"sessionID":"ses_285f75901ffeIBkgt46cBvDW9m","part":{"id":"prt_d7a08b2aa001L5iqCArbuR0fBe","messageID":"msg_d7a08a7e0001nH8w0Cg8Gb6uzw","sessionID":"ses_285f75901ffeIBkgt46cBvDW9m","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/.sdd_prompt.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: Write delta-spec.md (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios) for the agentcube project:\n2: \n3: AR: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\n4: Module: pkg/store\n5: Language: Go\n6: Size: S\n7: \n8: Base specs:\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\n10: # client-go library\n11: \n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\n13: \n14: ## Clientset\n15: \n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n17: \n18: ```go\n19: type Interface interface {\n20: \tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n21: \tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n22: }\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### `Clientset` struct\n26: \n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\n28: \n29: **Constructors**\n30: \n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n35: \n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n37: \n38: ---\n39: \n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\n41: \n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`)\n43: \n44: ```go\n45: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n46: \tRESTClient() rest.Interface\n47: \tAgentRuntimesGetter\n48: \tCodeInterpretersGetter\n49: }\n50: ```\n51: \n52: `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` implements this interface. REST defaults: `GroupVersion` = `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.SchemeGroupVersion, `APIPath` = `/apis`, negotiated serializer from `clientset/versioned/scheme`.\n53: \n54: ### `AgentRuntimesGetter` / `AgentRuntimeInterface` (`.../agentruntime.go`)\n55: \n56: ```go\n57: type AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n58: \tAgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n59: }\n60: \n61: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n62: \tCreate(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n63: \tUpdate(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n64: \tUpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n65: \tDelete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n66: \tDeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n67: \tGet(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n68: \tList(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n69: \tWatch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n70: \tPatch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n71: \tAgentRuntimeExpansion\n72: }\n73: ```\n74: \n75: REST resource plural: **`agentruntimes`**.\n76: \n77: ### `CodeInterpretersGetter` / `CodeInterpreterInterface` (`.../codeinterpreter.go`)\n78: \n79: Same met